description:
Darkness Radio presents Haunted: Lindsey Higgins' Past Lives, Alien Abductions, & Ghostly Visitations with Co-Authors Dan Baldwin and George Sewell!

Lindsey Higgins was just a little girl running around a balcony in Louisiana, when her parents scooped her up and asked her how she got out of the house. She claimed an invisible friend named Morlock lifted an incredibly heavy double paned window and let her out! From there, the mystery only deepened! After a call to George Sewell, Lindsey began to discover certain things about her past lives, her relationship with "Morlock", and a past life pact made with the "sky people"...

Get the book, "Paranormal Pendulum III: The Abduction of Lindsey Higgins..." here: https://amzn.to/3q0oBHj
